OL,3,CDisgraced politician offers
OL,4,Cresignation after conviction for child
OL,5,Csex offences
OL,7,FGuernsey politician Jonathan Le Tocq
OL,8,Fhas submitted his resignation after
OL,9,Fpleading guilty to 15 sexual offences,
OL,10,Fincluding possessing more than 2,400
OL,11,Findecent images of children.
OL,13,FThe disgraced politician wrote to the
OL,14,FStates Assembly the day he pleaded
OL,15,Fguilty to the offences in Guernsey's
OL,16,FRoyal Court, but details have only
OL,17,Fbeen published five days later.
