OL,7,FThe States Assembly will now have to
OL,8,Fdebate and vote on whether to accept
OL,9,Fit. That vote will be on December 17th
OL,10,Fand until that time Le Tocq will still
OL,11,Fbe paid.
OL,13,FThe 61 year old pleaded guilty to all
OL,14,Fcounts against him on December 4th,
OL,15,Fwhich included making indecent images
OL,16,Fof children, possessing extreme
OL,17,Fpornographic images, and sending
OL,18,Findecent images through social media
OL,19,Faccounts on X.
