OL,7,F"I'd reiterate that I'm still hoping
OL,8,Fthat Le Tocq will choose to do the
OL,9,Fright thing, but it is right that we
OL,10,Falso consider whether our laws and our
OL,11,Fother rules around this need to change.
OL,13,F"I don't think we should be making
OL,14,Fknee-jerk reactions on what is a very
OL,15,Femotional and difficult period. It
OL,16,Fneeds a serious and careful
OL,17,Fconsideration."
OL,19,FLe Tocq's resignation will trigger the
OL,20,Fisland's first-ever by-election under
OL,21,Fthe island-wide voting system.
