OL,7,FDeputy de Sausmarez told ITV News that
OL,8,Fone of the first States Assembly
OL,9,Fdebates this political term determined
OL,10,Fa by-election would be "significantly
OL,11,Fless costly than the original
OL,12,Festimates suggested".
OL,14,FThe Chief Minister also explained that
OL,15,Fvetting procedures would also go some
OL,16,Fway to rebuilding trust in the States
OL,17,Ffollowing Le Tocq's guilty pleas.
