OL,7,F"The actions of one individual are not
OL,8,Freflective of the government of the
OL,9,FStates as a whole. What really matters
OL,10,Fis how we respond to those actions.
OL,12,F"I think we can take a silver lining
OL,13,Ffrom this awful situation, it is that
OL,14,Fwe have seen that nobody is above the
OL,15,Flaw, no matter how senior. No matter
OL,16,Ftheir status, they can be held to
OL,17,Fproper and just account."
